</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>在？宁搁这给👴整<a href="/rat-s-nest-hub">鼠巢</a>呢——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meowait" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4274367); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4274367&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="Meowait" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4274367)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meowait" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4274367); return false;">Meowait</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>？啥b——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zihao-huang" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3677740); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3677740&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="Zihao Huang" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3677740)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zihao-huang" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3677740); return false;">Zihao Huang</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>啥β 不许学我开留言板 待会先杀鹿子再杀你 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moyo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2538335); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2538335&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="Moyo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2538335)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/moyo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2538335); return false;">Moyo</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>本公司高价回收二手882、093、1004、废旧aic，同时承接深红之王锁链抛光/打腊，修理康德计数器，清洗时间槽，高空作业擦洗星球表面逆模因，173喷漆，欲肉仪式材料保养，破碎之神设计，SCP-4001保养及维护，K级情景修复，3999形状改造及白天黑夜颠倒业务，并批发500、914，量大从优，团购7折。详情请致电11451481093——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ninth-bb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4370469); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4370469&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="Ninth BB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4370469)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ninth-bb" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4370469); return false;">Ninth BB</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>(窥视)——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justaswelljar-pepper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4301969); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4301969&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="JustAswellJar Pepper" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4301969)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/justaswelljar-pepper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4301969); return false;">JustAswellJar Pepper</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>假设我们从一数到三又从三数到一，你会发现我们不过浪费了人生的六秒钟。没有那么多意义可寻，他是过街老鼠，而我们不过都是乐子而已。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drsee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2928788); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2928788&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="DrSee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2928788)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drsee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2928788); return false;">DrSee</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>嘟啦啦啦啦啦啦啦啦，踩一脚。(≧▽≦)――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>不准跳段街舞？我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了我急了。<br />
一天，鱼徒拿着海盗报一则关于克尔凯郭尔的报纸，高高兴兴地走在街上，撞见了尼采，他问：尼采哥哥，上帝去哪了？<br />
尼采：上帝死了。<br />
鱼徒听闻上帝死了的消息，捧腹大笑，接着陀思妥耶夫斯基也来了，鱼徒问：我要当超人。<br />
陀思妥耶夫斯基没有说什么，给了鱼徒一本《罪与罚》。<br />
鱼徒晚上回家的时候，看见弗兰兹·卡夫卡和马克斯·勃罗德在烧书，鱼徒高兴地过去把《罪与罚》一并烧去。<br />
隔天，鱼徒见到了德里达。<br />
鱼徒：德里达叔叔，德里达叔叔，Error小朋友去哪了？<br />
德里达抹了抹泪水，回复道：唉，被解构了。<br />
鱼徒睡了，他在梦里，走在静静的顿河，告别肖洛霍夫。――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rorrerd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3453246); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3453246&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="rorrErD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3453246)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rorrerd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3453246); return false;">rorrErD</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>鱼徒睡了，他在梦里，走在静静的顿河，告别肖洛霍夫。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>爷在重写590了，在写了，别骂了——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aieditor059" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872755); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2872755&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="AIeditor059" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2872755)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aieditor059" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2872755); return false;">AIeditor059</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>🐟徒，我的文字大麻&#8230;&#8230;——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wuhu-horse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4092253); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4092253&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608826595" alt="WuHu Horse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4092253)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wuhu-horse" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4092253); return false;">WuHu Horse</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>Rest In Pocky my kid&#8230;&#8230;——<span class="error-inline"><em>HappyStorm Zhang</em> does not match any existing user name</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
